release_note: You asked for it we built it Introducing Likes! Now you can encourage fellow GoodVibes community members in their path to reduce anxiety by engaging directly with their entries.
A completely re designed user experience featuring native SwiftUI elements that helps users quickly dive into the journaling experience
Word counter as well as clearer prompts
Squashing urgent bug that is causing the app to crash
Total overhaul based on user feedback. New features include multiple categories quick start positivity stress hard decisions cleaner UI and the ability to submit multiple prompts per day.
